  "title": "General worker or Technician",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p>\n<p>The person will be working with site personnel, site activities and be highly involved in the following aspects of the business but not limited to the below:</p>\n<p>· Support to Engineer &amp; Manager in carrying out general works.</p>\n<p>· Able to help supervise and control sub-contractors to carry out their works.</p>\n<p>· Undertake ad-hoc duties as assigned.</p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Secondary school / NITEC in any Engineering</p>\n<p>· Minimum 1 years of working experience in the related field is preferred</p>\n<p>· Possess relevant safety certificates (BCSS) will be an advantage</p>\n<p>· Willing to travel based on the project site.</p>\n<p>· Ability to communicate in English</p>\n<p>· Ability to work independently and ensure task given is completed in time</p>\n<p>· Highly communicative and self-motivated individual personality</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please submit your application.</p>\n<p>Please state your</p>\n<p>· Last drawn &amp; Expected salary</p>\n<p>· Notice Period / Availability</p>\n<p>(We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified)</p>",
